      • updateStoreWithTempVar

        public void updateStoreWithTempVar​(org.checkerframework.dataflow.analysis.TransferResult<org.checkerframework.common.accumulation.AccumulationValue,​org.checkerframework.common.accumulation.AccumulationStore> result,
                                   org.checkerframework.dataflow.cfg.node.Node node)
        This method either creates or looks up the temp var t for node, and then updates the store to give t the same type as node. Temporary variables are supported for expressions throughout this checker (and the Must Call Checker) to enable refinement of their types. See the documentation of MustCallConsistencyAnalyzer for more details.
        Parameters:
        node - the node to be assigned to a temporary variable
        result - the transfer result containing the store to be modified
